Grammar

    0 $accept: function $end

    1 function: function_header variables body

    2 function_header: FUNCTION IDENTIFIER optional_parameters RETURNS type ';'
    3                | FUNCTION IDENTIFIER error ';'

    4 optional_parameters: parameters
    5                    | %empty

    6 parameters: parameters ',' parameter
    7           | parameter

    8 parameter: IDENTIFIER ':' type

    9 variables: variables variable
   10          | %empty

   11 variable: IDENTIFIER ':' type IS statement_
   12         | IDENTIFIER ':' LIST OF type IS list ';'
   13         | IDENTIFIER error IS statement_

   14 type: INTEGER
   15     | REAL
   16     | CHARACTER

   17 list: '(' expressions ')'

   18 expressions: expressions ',' expression
   19            | expression

   20 body: BEGIN_ statement_ END ';'

   21 statement_: statement ';'
   22           | error ';'

   23 statement: expression
   24          | WHEN condition ',' expression ':' expression
   25          | WHEN error ';'
   26          | SWITCH expression IS cases OTHERS ARROW statement_ ENDSWITCH
   27          | IF condition THEN statement_ elsif_clauses ELSE statement_ ENDIF
   28          | FOLD direction operator list_choice ENDFOLD

   29 elsif_clauses: elsif_clauses ELSIF condition THEN statement_
   30              | %empty

   31 cases: cases case
   32      | %empty

   33 case: CASE INT_LITERAL ARROW statement_
   34     | CASE error ARROW statement_

   35 direction: LEFT
   36          | RIGHT

   37 operator: ADDOP
   38         | MULOP

   39 list_choice: list
   40            | IDENTIFIER

   41 condition: or_condition

   42 or_condition: or_condition OROP and_condition
   43             | and_condition

   44 and_condition: and_condition ANDOP not_condition
   45              | not_condition

   46 not_condition: NOTOP not_condition
   47              | relation

   48 relation: '(' condition ')'
   49         | expression RELOP expression

   50 expression: expression ADDOP term
   51           | term

   52 term: term MULOP power
   53     | term MODOP power
   54     | power

   55 power: unary EXPOP power
   56      | unary

   57 unary: NEGOP unary
   58      | primary

   59 primary: '(' expression ')'
   60        | INT_LITERAL
   61        | REAL_LITERAL
   62        | CHAR_LITERAL
   63        | IDENTIFIER '(' expression ')'
   64        | IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '(' (40) 17 48 59 63
    ')' (41) 17 48 59 63
    ',' (44) 6 18 24
    ':' (58) 8 11 12 24
    ';' (59) 2 3 12 20 21 22 25
    error (256) 3 13 22 25 34
    IDENTIFIER <iden> (258) 2 3 8 11 12 13 40 63 64
    INT_LITERAL <type> (259) 33 60
    REAL_LITERAL <type> (260) 61
    CHAR_LITERAL <type> (261) 62
    ADDOP (262) 37 50
    MULOP (263) 38 52
    MODOP (264) 53
    EXPOP (265) 55
    NEGOP (266) 57
    ANDOP (267) 44
    OROP (268) 42
    NOTOP (269) 46
    RELOP (270) 49
    ARROW (271) 26 33 34
    BEGIN_ (272) 20
    CASE (273) 33 34
    CHARACTER (274) 16
    ELSE (275) 27
    ELSIF (276) 29
    END (277) 20
    ENDIF (278) 27
    ENDFOLD (279) 28
    ENDSWITCH (280) 26
    FOLD (281) 28
    FUNCTION (282) 2 3
    IF (283) 27
    INTEGER (284) 14
    IS (285) 11 12 13 26
    LEFT (286) 35
    LIST (287) 12
    OF (288) 12
    OTHERS (289) 26
    REAL (290) 15
    RETURNS (291) 2
    RIGHT (292) 36
    SWITCH (293) 26
    THEN (294) 27 29
    WHEN (295) 24 25


Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

    $accept (46)
        on left: 0
    function <type> (47)
        on left: 1
        on right: 0
    function_header (48)
        on left: 2 3
        on right: 1
    optional_parameters <type> (49)
        on left: 4 5
        on right: 2
    parameters <type> (50)
        on left: 6 7
        on right: 4 6
